r thrilling playing technique in her live shows.\rBorn in Kyiv Ukraine, Kateryna first developed the love and interest in playing the harp at age 7 and later went onto furthering her passion by attending and graduating with Honors at the Kiev Institute of Music R.M. Gliera, receiving the Junior Specialist and Bachelors Degree in Harp performance.\rShe has performed with orchestras, among them the “Symfomania”, performing on a Lyon &amp; Healy electro harp in a Rock Ensemble using digital processors and effects to alter the sound of the Harp. Throughout her time with the group, She has composed several original pieces for the Ensemble and also as a solo artist; moreover, she has performed with “Symfomania” to crowds as large as 10,000 people and completed over a 100 performances. After touring Europe with the “Symfomania” in 2016, Kateryna moved to Dubai to showcase her talent, performing at many prestigious events and 5 Star hotels around the UAE. Throughout her stay, Kateryna brought to life the cultural diversity in Dubai through her extensive background and experience in Middle Eastern, Western and Asian Music, with genres ranging from Classical, Pop, Rock, Bollywood, Arabic and more!\rWith a strong social media following of over 17000+ Instagram followers, she continues to strive for excellence and to push the boundaries of music with an honorable quest of bringing happiness and beauty to the world through her unique music and performances.\rHarpist in Dubai the best option to hire for your corporate events, Western, Arabic and Indian wedding ceremony, TV shows, concerts, and more.\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:10:\"1408977275\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:33:\"KG Production &amp; Events FZ LLC\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:2:\"50\";s:3:\"iso\";s:3:\"100\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:5:\"0.005\";s:5:\"title\";s:23:\"Harpist in Dubai - Kate\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:12:{i:0;s:16:\"Harpist in Dubai\";i:1;s:17:\"Abu Dhabi artists\";i:2;s:11:\"Harp playe